title: Ashtralle Just Missoo
description:
Ashtralle Just Missoo Kannada:???????????? ????? ???????;English:Just Missed In Time is a 2014 Indian Kannada-Language film that is Rohit Padaki's directorial Debut.Music is composed by Immanuel Richard and Tejas. This film was made without any investment by group of youngsters and is the first Zero Budget movie in India which has now made way to lot of enthusiasts to take up Indie films seriously.Naveen,Apeksha,Rohit Padaki,Girija Lokesh are in the lead role.
PLOT:Shankru,an out of sorts youngster leads a carefree life.He is least bothered about his mother's hardships to bring him up.Addicted to all the bad things in life,he is thrown out of his house for his good. He gets into a job through his friend and how things change when he falls in love with Veda, makes the whole story a must watch.Its a movie filled with laughter and drama which will entertain you through out. Jogayya a character reflecting Shankru's fate plays a major role in his life with highs and lows with confusions.
